## Common Workflows

### New Character Setup
1. Create base [[Character Sheet|templates/character/character_sheet]]
2. Add [[Combat Sheet|templates/character/combat_character_sheet]]
3. Set up relevant specialty trackers:
   * Combat: [[Combat Technique Tracker|templates/combat/combat_technique_tracker]]
   * Social: [[Social Identity Tracker|templates/social/social_identity_tracker]]
   * Spiritual: [[Spiritual Practice Tracker|templates/spiritual/spiritual_practice_tracker]]

### Quest Management
1. Create quest in [[Quest Tracker|templates/quests/quest_tracker_template]]
2. Link relevant NPCs in [[Social Relationship Tracker|templates/social/social_relationship_tracker]]
3. Prepare needed encounter templates
4. Track progress and updates

### Travel Planning
1. Fill [[Travel Template|templates/activities/travel_template]]
2. Prepare potential encounters
3. Track resources and supplies
4. Note discoveries and events

